snippet.title: Falcon Beertender E-Game (Windows game 2000)
snippet.description:
Falcon Beertender is a simple Swedish game by E-Game.
The main player has to give a glass of beer to a customer and receive the empty glass.
You make them go to the left of the game screen absolutely.
